## JSONStore.set property

Set a key-val to `Storage`<!-- -->, but jsonify the value.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
set: (key: string, payload: any) => void;
```

## Example


```ts
local.set('foo', { a: 123 })
local.get('foo') // => { a: 123 }

```
